      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "The Ultimate Fight?",
        "Client": "Childish Researcher",
        "Description": "Whooooooa! Rajang spotted in\r\nthe Flooded Forest!? And there\u0027s\r\ntwo of \u0027em! Oh, boy! Oh, boy! I\u0027m\r\ngonna go see Rajang! I\u0027m gonna\r\ngo see\u2014 Hey! What are you\r\nwaitin\u0027 for? Let\u0027s go see \u0027em!\r\nWe\u0027re gonna see Rajang!",
